es/goods, belts, wallets, etc.; and PVC films and sheeting products that are used in shower curtains, side door panels/sun visor, stationary, insulation tapes, rainwear, etc. It also offers blister free, pharma strip, biaxially oriented polypropylene, and cast polypropylene foils; glassine paper; and kaneka gemlac resins. The company serves commercial, industrial, pharmaceutical, and food processing industries. Amco India Limited was incorporated in 1987 and is based in Noida, India."}}